issue.title: Wiki search v2
issue.body:
I think I fixed the issue of the potential infinite loop. If a tag does not have a directly related wiki page, meaning there is no article with the same title, I have it return a default response string. As for the issue of not working in images, I think that's a Clarifai issue? 
Finally, I changed which Wikimedia API we are using since it returns what we want and has more info when we search for something that has multiple pages.

issue.title: Wiki search v2
issue.body: Updated version to handle search requests that do not return a definitive search result. This happens when a Wiki search has multiple results or the search query does not have a Wiki page.
